$OpenBSD: patch-pango_opentype_hb-buffer_h,v 1.1 2011/03/22 09:41:15 jasper Exp $

Security fix for CVE-2011-0064
Pango "hb_buffer_ensure()" Memory Reallocation Vulnerability

Fix backported from harfbuzz git, via redhat bz: #678563
https://bugzilla.redhat.com/attachment.cgi?id=480386

--- pango/opentype/hb-buffer.h.orig	Tue Feb  9 13:06:28 2010
+++ pango/opentype/hb-buffer.h	Tue Mar 22 10:27:42 2011
@@ -94,7 +94,7 @@ hb_buffer_clear (hb_buffer_t *buffer);
 void
 hb_buffer_clear_positions (hb_buffer_t *buffer);
 
-void
+hb_bool_t
 hb_buffer_ensure (hb_buffer_t  *buffer,
 		  unsigned int  size);
 
